<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">When you link a MailChimp account, all of the lists in your account will be imported for analysis. With a linked account, you can always take advantage of Free Email Assurance and monitor your lists on a daily basis. <\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">If you purchase a One-Time Tune Up for a list, results will &nbsp;be automatically synced back to the ESP and you can continuously monitor your list's status. If you purchase Email Assurance PLUS for a list, list maintenance is on auto-pilot and your list will be analyzed and updated daily.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">After making a purchase,&nbsp;results will be automatically synced back to your MailChimp account.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\"><strong>What's updated in your MailChimp account:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">When lists are synced back&nbsp;all of your original information will be re-imported in your MailChimp account.&nbsp;All&nbsp;email addresses within your list will be updated and indexed with Email Assurance Grades from your&nbsp;Report Card.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">If you choose to unsubscribe all F grades we'll do that for you, but addresses will not be deleted from your MailChimp account. Invalid emails are given an Email Assurance Grade of F.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\"><strong>Creating Segments:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">We recommend creating segments within your MailChimp account as soon as you purchase the first list. Create segments for 'Safe to Send', 'Accepts All', and Indeterminate' emails. (If you choose to keep addresses with F grades, create a 'Do Not Send' segment)<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\"><a href=\"\/hc\/en-us\/articles\/200879139-How-do-I-segment-a-list-in-my-MailChimp-account-\" target=\"_blank\">How do I segment a list in MailChimp?&nbsp;<\/a><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.666666984558105px; font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-color-black\">Login to&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #1155cc; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http:\/\/datavalidation.com\/login\" target=\"_blank\">My Account<\/a>&nbsp;| Go&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #1155cc; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"http:\/\/datavalidation.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">DataValidation.com<\/a><\/span><\/p>",
